CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 23, 1956, pg. A1, reads: "Graduate Nurse - While Oliver K. Fry and Peter A. Schessler of the Raymond P. Cronin VFW Post 267 observe, Miss Elizabeth Moore of Clairton receives a gift from Post Commander James P. A. Bullotta shortly before she graduated from St. Francis Hospital, where she completed a scholarship given her by the veterans' post. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: James P. A. Bullotta offering gift to newly graduated nurse Elizabeth Moore, with Oliver K. Fry and Peter A. Schessler from Raymond P. Cronin VFW Post 267 observing
